text: Novofyodorovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Satyyevsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 63 as of 2010. There are2 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 8 km from Satyyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Novofyodorovka, Miyakinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
